Package: framedListeningNLP
Title: Framed Listening — NLP Analysis Pipeline
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-04-15
Authors@R: person("Hazel A.", "van der Walle",
                  email = "hazel.a.vanderwalle@durham.ac.uk",
                  role  = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Quarto-based NLP analysis pipeline for the Framed Listening
    research project (Durham University, Music). Analyses semantic
    similarity of music-influenced mental content (MIMC) using TF-IDF,
    Word2Vec, and sentence embedding models. Four pipelines:
    text preprocessing, TF-IDF (combMIMC), sentence embeddings (individual),
    and cross-model comparison.
URL: https://github.com/HazelvdW/context-framed-listening
